      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JANE'S JET (2) goes very well here starting nine times for three wins and five minors. In the money last time at Q Lakeside (22.02) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 0.8 lengths second. Rates on top and should go close. BLACK RASPBERRY (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a third place finish (30.41) at Q Parklands the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Has ability and is one of the better chances. WALKING CARPET (7) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, rewarded with a win last time at this track over 366m. Bold showing expected again. MORE THAN MERRY (3) cannot be left out over a shorter journey.",
